Class BuiltUserRoleMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.raweng.built.BuiltUserRoleMapper

  • public class BuiltUserRoleMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    BuiltUserRoleMapper is used to create, update and delete built user role mapper on the Built.io Backend server.
